Body:
Description: Hello, we have followed all of the documentation for installing endpoint protector on macs.  It installs but we are unable to get it to apply the provided configuration and connect to the server.  Is it possible to setup a troubleshooting call to resolve our issue?

The VM died when I went to appliance->server info
What We've Learned Updated: Customer used different script than the JAMF ones. Provided correct scripts.
Next Steps Updated: 03Feb: Waiting on customer to mass re-deploy the agents and see if they connect to the EPP server now.
